{"tid":789052,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"男子瑞和街網吧遭刀煞按地斬手腳　警查半日拘2漢","createTime":"2018-08-22T03:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:17:52.000Z","uid":38189,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"862ce4732e1c8a4e51e2e723af1d529b70db66d9","tid":789052,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"觀塘一間網吧發生斬人血案。今晨5時許，一名姓張（25歲）男子與一名友人於瑞和街19號一間樓上網吧消遣，期間事主與一名男子因故發生爭執，對方悻然離去，隨後帶同1名男子返回，一人將事主推跌按在地上，另一人拔出利刀斬傷其右手及右腳，兇徒得手後逃離現場，事主同行友人致電報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕至，將傷者送院治理，並翻查「天眼」緝兇。經調查後，至下午5時許，在秀茂坪拘捕2名分別姓馮(25歲)及姓蔡(26歲)男子，涉嫌傷人，初步調查顯示2男有黑社會背景，現正被通宵扣查，案件交由觀塘警區反黑組跟進。"},{"pid":"78659523216d33f977c850ea77bc6af696f083f9","tid":789052,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2750b329e6833a38c342693ba713e2df9c62799","tid":789052,"uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"瑞和街又中！"},{"pid":"b149beb9e76eb898f661b4ca036eb6fc2c4c3476","tid":789052,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78659523216d33f977c850ea77bc6af696f083f9","tid":789052,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544fc637f212d694710fbf30d4d00e7b28723eb5","tid":789052,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b149beb9e76eb898f661b4ca036eb6fc2c4c3476","tid":789052,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78659523216d33f977c850ea77bc6af696f083f9","tid":78